### Code Characteristics Metrics API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@userId = 1

### 1. Get code characteristics for the last 30 days (default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/{{userId}}/metrics/code-characteristics
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get code characteristics for the last 7 days
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/{{userId}}/metrics/code-characteristics?windowDays=7
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Get code characteristics for the last 90 days
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/{{userId}}/metrics/code-characteristics?windowDays=90
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Get code characteristics for the last 14 days (bi-weekly sprint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/{{userId}}/metrics/code-characteristics?windowDays=14
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Error: Invalid user ID (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/99999/metrics/code-characteristics?windowDays=30
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Error: Invalid window days - zero (should return 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/{{userId}}/metrics/code-characteristics?windowDays=0
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Error: Invalid window days - negative (should return 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/{{userId}}/metrics/code-characteristics?windowDays=-5
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Error: Window days exceeds maximum (should return 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/{{userId}}/metrics/code-characteristics?windowDays=400
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. Get code characteristics for a different user
@userId2 = 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/{{userId2}}/metrics/code-characteristics?windowDays=30
Accept: application/json

###

### 10. Get code characteristics for the last 60 days (quarterly review)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/{{userId}}/metrics/code-characteristics?windowDays=60
Accept: application/json

###
